data.meta_description: Crazy Little Thing Called Love！This is a Thai film about first love. This film had aroused my resonance, because I had a similar experience with Nam. I pretend casual encounters with him, like Nam did in the movie. I became very nervous when I was in front of him; when others are talking about him I pretend don’t care about what they saying, in fact, I’ve been listening to them. (By the way. Mario is sooooo cute!!)
